    "stdyInfo": {
      "abstract": [
        {
          "contentType": "purpose",
          "lang": "fr",
          "value": "Démontrer que le risque de cancer de l’œsophage augmente selon le type de tabac ou d'alcool consommé. Définir une classification des différents types de tabac et d'alcool pour le risque du cancer de l’œsophage. Démontrer que certaines habitudes alimentaires augmentent le risque de cancer de l’œsophage."
        },
        {
          "contentType": "purpose",
          "lang": "en",
          "value": "To demonstrate that the risk of cancer of the oesophagus increases according to types of tobacco and alcohol use. To classify different types of tobacco and alcohol in accordance to risk of cancer of the oesophagus. To demonstrate certain dietary habits that increase the risk of cancer of the oesophagus."
        }
      ],
